	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Nice job on the LCD.  I've considered adding one for a project I have in mind as well.  I'm just afraid I'd make a mess out of the NES case though since I don't have a quality dremel.  I guess that's what I get for buying something called RotoMatic.
<br />
<br />The thing that stood out to me though in your pics, and what made me do a double-take, is the fact that you have four controller ports!  While this might be a normal mod around these parts, I haven't seen such a thing before.  I would assume it's using the same extra shift registers deal as the Four Score, though I can't see what it's connected to to know exactly what you've done.

		

